                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/81680364/">苍城子</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-08-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">其实有些书只要你用心去读，总会有收获。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

